snippet.textDisplay:
Okay. I know I'm going to get a lot of hate for saying this, but I'm going to say it anyway. I listened to this song without watching the video first and I felt that this song is ridiculously overrated. Then I read the comments and it pissed me off even more. I'm pressing the dislike button. 
Regarding all the people praising the female lead singer's "voice" and "talent", I'm baffled by how easily your mind get swayed by the sight of a pretty looking girl. I mean, for God's sake, think about it for a moment - would you have praised the singer's "voice" and "talent" if she was ugly as fuck? Be honest with yourself. Forget praising, you wouldn't even have noticed her. 
My personal opinion is that this song sucks; has poor lyrics, no structure, no soul and the female singer isn't opening up her voice at all.
